==English==
===Noun===
'''dextrin'''
#{{chemistry}} a range of [[polymer]]s of [[glucose]], intermediate in complexity between [[maltose]] and [[starch]], produced by the [[enzymatic]] [[hydrolysis]] of starch; used commercially as [[adhesive]]s

===Synonyms===
*[[E1400]] when used as a [[food additive]]

